<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>You are a mid-tier wizard at Dawnstar-Riften-Morthal (DRM) Consulting. The
company is huge, responsible for most of the types of magic in the world. Their
work is exported all around the world and DRM is a byword for quality.</p>

<p>There's a large sign on the office wall with the following:</p>

